<item>
            <title>[LU-587] mgs have corrupted config llog but forbid to re-register a target</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-587</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;after hard reset mgs configuration llog can truncated. in case OST config llog also corrupted it&apos;s prevent ost to be started. Same situation can be occurred with MDT also.&lt;br/&gt;
it&apos;s easy replicated by truncate mgs config llog to zero.&lt;br/&gt;
In that case mgs have bit set - &apos;that target registered&apos; and forbid to re-register target, but none configuration send to OST.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>lustre 2.1/RHEL6 </environment>
